{"lemma":"صَبِيٌّ","slug":"صَبِيٌّ","root":"ص.ب.#","root_slug":"ص-ب-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ب-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صَبِيّ","root":"صبو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23746"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8C%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rejuvenate, to make youthful again","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23746","headword_ar":"صَبِىٌّ","root":"Sbw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A youth, boy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulaAmN","text_ar":"غُلَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young male child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before he is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulaAm","text_ar":"غُلَام"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one that has not yet been weaned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) so called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the time of his birth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAbK","text_ar":"صَابٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~N","text_ar":"صَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; these two words being like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAdirN","text_ar":"قَادِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadiyrN","text_ar":"قَدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. of the former is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyapN","text_ar":"صِبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a pl. of pauc., in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"is changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the kesreh before it, like as is said in the M respecting another of the pls.,] (S, M, Msb, K, but not in the CK,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibowapN","text_ar":"صِبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabowapN","text_ar":"صَبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuboyapN","text_ar":"صُبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaboyapN","text_ar":"صَبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, but not in the CK,) [or rather the last two are quasi-pl. ns.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobK","text_ar":"اَصْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[another pl. of pauc.] (K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobiyapN","text_ar":"اَصْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also a pl. of pauc.], (M, K,) but this last is said by J to have been unused, because the usage of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyapN","text_ar":"صِبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"rendered it needless, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyaAnN","text_ar":"صِبْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K, but not in the CK,) in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"is changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the kesreh before it, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuboyaAnN","text_ar":"صُبْيَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) as some say, preserving the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"notwithstanding the dammeh, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SibowaAnN","text_ar":"صِبْوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, but not in the CK,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SubowaAnN","text_ar":"صُبْوَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and [ISd says,] accord. to Sb, the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyapN","text_ar":"صِبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSayobiyapN","text_ar":"اُصَيْبِيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobiyapN","text_ar":"اَصْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Subay~apN","text_ar":"صُبَيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", each irreg.; but in my opinion,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Subay~apN","text_ar":"صُبَيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyapN","text_ar":"صِبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSayobiyapN","text_ar":"اُصَيْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobiyapN","text_ar":"اَصْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) [J says,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uSayobiyapN","text_ar":"اُصَيْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in poetry as being the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobiyapN","text_ar":"اَصْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sabiy~apN","text_ar":"صَبِيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young woman, girl,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female child;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) and so too, [sometimes,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~N","text_ar":"صَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabaAyaA","text_ar":"صَبَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u AlS~iboyaAni","text_ar":"اُمُّ الصِّبْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a term applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The flatus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flatulence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~iyHu","text_ar":"الرِّيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is incident to children."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Am","text_ar":"ام"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [Golius, in that art., explains it as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Larva, terriculamentum puerorum;"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the authority of Meyd.: and also as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Epilepsy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the authority of Ibn-Beytár.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~N","text_ar":"صَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pupil of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) but Kr ascribes this meaning to the vulgar. (M.) ―         -b4-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of each of the jaw-bones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) i. e. (TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abiy~aAni","text_ar":"الصَّبِيَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two extremities of the two jaw-bones"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, TA) of the camel and of other animals: or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two edges curving outwards from the middle of the two jaw-bones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) or, accord. to the A,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thin portions of the two extremities thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is [said to be] tropical. (TA.) And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bone below the lobe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lobule, of each of the two ears:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, as some say, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head of the bone that is below the lobe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lobule, of each of the two ears by the space of about three fingers put together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b5-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~","text_ar":"حَدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") of the sword: (M, K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ridge"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof, (M, TA, in the copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo gayorihi","text_ar":"اَوْ غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awo Eayoruhu","text_ar":"اَوْ عَيْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which rises in"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"along"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its middle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA;) and likewise of a spear-head: (M, TA:) or, accord. to the A, that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"below,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exclusive of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna","text_ar":"دُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zubap","text_ar":"ظُبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the human foot; (M, A, TA; in the copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osu Alqawomi","text_ar":"رَاْسُ القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osu Alqadami","text_ar":"رَاْسُ القَدَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; TA;) i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thereof]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaArap","text_ar":"حِمَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the toes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~abiy~aAni","text_ar":"الصَّبِيَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two sides of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's saddle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b7-  It is also said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyaAnu Aljaliydi","text_ar":"صِبْيَانُ الجَلِيدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The grains of hoar-frost that resemble pearls:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiboyaAnu AlmaTari","text_ar":"صِبْيَانُ المَطَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the small drops of rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to the author of the “ Khasáïl, ” it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Siy^obaAn","text_ar":"صِيْبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suw^aAbapN","text_ar":"صُوَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.], with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"and then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","M","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}